Sentencas: The influence of Co3O4 as a sintering aid for a series of cobalt-containing perovskite oxides on the microstructure and electrical properties have been investigated.
Titulo: Interlayer-free electrodes for IT-SOFCs by applying Co3O4 as sintering aid

Sentencas: X-ray diffraction and scanning electron microscopic results showed that well connected electrode particles with firm adhesion to the 8 mol% yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte surface were realized at a temperature free from interfacial phase reaction.
Titulo: Interlayer-free electrodes for IT-SOFCs by applying Co3O4 as sintering aid

Sentencas: Both ohmic and polarization resistances of symmetric cells by adopting YSZ electrolyte, measured by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy, were much lower than that without adding Co3O4.
Titulo: Interlayer-free electrodes for IT-SOFCs by applying Co3O4 as sintering aid

Sentencas: The peak power density of 1176 mW cm(-2) at 750 degrees C was achieved when La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta + Co3O4 was selected as a representative cobaltite cathode, which is much higher than a similar fuel cell with the cathode fabricated by a conventional way.
Titulo: Interlayer-free electrodes for IT-SOFCs by applying Co3O4 as sintering aid

Sentencas: Fabrication of interlayer-free electrodes by applying Co3O4 as a sintering aid is very simple and general, applicable for a wide range of cobalt-containing electrode materials.
Titulo: Interlayer-free electrodes for IT-SOFCs by applying Co3O4 as sintering aid
